Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:36.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}淺波輕搖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:47.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}蕩漾起我的心潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:03.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}靜靜地　靜靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:14.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心里有了一絲預感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 今天一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該有些別的話可以對我說吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:10.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:18.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我錢放進去了但東西卻沒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因為這個相當舊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想拍攝黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:43.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 夜晚變成藍天的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚變成藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 再一會兒就可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:10.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄豆湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說什麼果汁出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在凌晨四點？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,凌晨四點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:23.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜她所賜 沒能拍到好不容易才有的晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晴空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍天空真是不會厭倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能會厭倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有如此之多的變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,人也有變化不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:47.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還問 我是來叫你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,班會要結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已經是這個時間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要急著去買東西對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個的話不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天已經買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:21.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說是女孩子反而會喜歡這種奇特的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾 差勁 沒品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然不懂得它的可愛之處…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你這自信是從哪裡來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要老做讓人不舒服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著 閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,睜開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是姊姊才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:04.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 小依總覺得有點彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 小依
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 真名總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 是姊姊 總是受到你的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我也是 我姊姊承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:26.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的話 一直陪著小依玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還是照樣有禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真的是姊妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,貧嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:37.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:42.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 今天順道去了別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去了別的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:06.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不喜歡蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我這邊也有禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天是你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我比平常更用心 挑了又挑才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天這個我本來還蠻有自信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 你這個自信是從哪裡來的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:33.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在轉換心情 來點上蠟燭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,相當大的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說教堂的鐘塔好像壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,教會？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 聽說是要被拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:04.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拍一下就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 依人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,熱衷於某事也要適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕不能吃 探病時間又沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為真的是太美了 忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊的生日對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:11.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以當作家人一起慶祝的只有依人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:12.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:19.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 什麼時候看夕陽不都是差不多的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空又不會逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一樣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是無藥可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:43.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,生薑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼 生薑之類的事先準備好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望能躲在讓我容易找的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到真的下大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:11.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又出不來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:16.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去便利商店不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡沒有賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不相信吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 這個拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:55.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 不要突然跑出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是覺得又傷到腳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再下小一點就馬上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就當作是被騙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,多買些儲藏起來會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不久就會停止販售的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很好喝的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡下雨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 應該是不喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為天空會變得看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原來喜歡天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 昨天也有做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡那樣做 拍攝不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 有很多天空的照片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也有一張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是一張而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的火燒雲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,火燒雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,染成暗紅色的雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也還有很多其它種類的天空喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,朝霞 晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晴天 萬里無雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,彩虹和黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雲的話 有棉花雲 雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,捲層雲 高層雲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是夏天的話 有積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是秋天的話 有鱗雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:08.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下次注意看一看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,朝霞 晚霞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晴天 萬里無雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,棉花雲 雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,捲層雲 高層雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是夏天的話 有積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是秋天的話 有鱗雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,菱狀雲 斷雲等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,菱狀雲 斷雲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 教了我許多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那把傘就送你了 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:13.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,發著呆 卻說有什麼要事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說是今天不去醫院直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然問他發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但淨是一些含含糊糊的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:48.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:52.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 8
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:18:00.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 非常抱歉 我懷疑你說的這張牌是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:18:00.08,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,她們玩的這個俗稱「說瞎話」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候不用這麼客氣地說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:13.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概今天也是跟這個有關係的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:15.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我等了這麼長的時間就只買來飯糰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊 無法實現的要求嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:34.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說想吃鵝肝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才帶你來這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:41.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最近鵝肝醬口味的飯糰在便利商店很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人傷腦筋的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大致的著眼點有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下次能遇到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:41.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興比想像的更早遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:33.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來玩文字接龍遊戲吧
